data.description: Beautiful Eastwood home in the Waterstone Estates subdivision. This home has been meticulously cared for and has had one owner since it was built in 2006. 4 spacious bedrooms with 2 bathrooms, 2 car garage and room to park a small travel trailer. The back patio is perfect for entertaining and relaxing with fire pit, hammock and small gazebo over the BBQ. Located in desirable neighborhood near schools, hospital, shopping, and parks. Landscaping in front and back yard is low maintenance including flowering lavender, blooming flowers, sprinkler system, and galvanized trough planters. Primary bedroom with walk in closet and access to the backyard through glass sliding doors. Roomy kitchen with oversized pantry. Interior doors and trim have just been repainted.
